t:
When I was young, I often overheard my parents talking about a twin sister who supposedly went missing from the hospital.
I never paid much attention to that.

Years later, as I'm in my bed eating this girl out, that familiar birthmark on her inner thighs makes me think otherwise.
c:
Did anyone go missing for you?



#missing #incest #oralsex #twins #missingsister





***SPOILER: Explanation***

I found my long lost sister, in an awkward situation.
Alternatively, the birthmark might be a coincidence.
